        {
            "title": "川普據稱將於下周公佈利用401(k)支付購房首付的計畫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 白宮國家經濟委員會主任凱文·哈塞特稱，美國總統唐納德·川普將於下周公佈一項計畫，允許參加401(k)退休計畫的儲蓄者動用其中部分資金，用作購買住房的首付款。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:哈塞特;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/哈塞特\">哈塞特</a>周五在福克斯商業頻道表示：「我們將允許人們從他們的401(k)中取出資金，用作首付款。」他還說：「總統將於下周在達沃斯公佈最終方案。」哈塞特所指的是川普計畫出席在瑞士達沃斯舉行的年度世界經濟論壇。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">哈塞特表示，如何將401(k)中的資產用於購房的具體操作機制仍在制定中。401(k)是一種由雇主發起的退休儲蓄計畫。他說：「比如說，你為一套房子支付了10%的首付款，然後你把房屋10%的淨值作為資產放入你的401(k)。這樣你的401(k)就會隨著時間推移而成長。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7cb10695-f6fb-39e8-b641-6088aa10e0e1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國決策圈人物志：「潛在的聯儲會主席」、川普首席經濟顧問哈塞特</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在新冠疫情之後，房價飆升、抵押貸款利率翻倍，住房成本——也是大多數美國人每月最大的一項支出——成為11月份國會中期選舉前的關鍵擔憂之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump to Unveil 401(k) Home Investment Plan at Davos Next Week</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Hadriana Lowenkron.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%93%9A%E7%A8%B1%E5%B0%87%E6%96%BC%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8401-k-%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E8%B3%BC%E6%88%BF%E9%A6%96%E4%BB%98%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-140023241.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 23:06:01",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國南方電網據悉有意競購巴西電力公司的輸電線路",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 知情人士表示，Actis LLP、中國南方電網以及Caisse de Depot et Placement du Quebec等公司均對可能收購巴西電力公司Energisa SA的輸電線路表示出興趣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">因討論未公開消息而要求匿名的知情人士表示，部分公司已聘請財務顧問，有約束力的要約預計將在1月下旬提交。知情人士還表示，在2024年被General Atlantic Co.收購的Actis正在與Banco Itau BBA合作。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7923257f-20cf-352d-a082-284a36890b3c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Actis和中國南方電網未立即回應置評請求，而Itau和Caisse拒絕發表評論。Energisa在發給彭博新聞社的電郵聲明中表示：「作為一家上市公司，按照我們的治理規定，我們不對交易和潛在的資產買賣意向發表評論。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Actis, China Power Grid Said Among Suitors for Energisa Assets</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Kathy Chen、Mathieu Dion.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E9%9B%BB%E7%B6%B2%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E7%AB%B6%E8%B3%BC%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E9%9B%BB%E5%8A%9B%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%9A%84%E8%BC%B8%E9%9B%BB%E7%B7%9A%E8%B7%AF-134402021.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 23:06:03",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "麥樸思稱目前金價沒有吸引力 認為中國股市的上漲具備可持續性",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 資深投資人<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:麥樸思;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/麥樸思\">麥樸思</a>(Mark Mobius)表示，在經歷歷史性大漲後，黃金已經變得不具吸引力。他警告稱，在市場大多仍堅定看多之際，美元若出現反彈，可能會削弱貴金屬的表現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位麥樸思新興機會基金(Mobius Emerging Opportunities Fund)的董事總經理周五在接受彭博電視採訪時說：「我不會在這個價位買入，這是肯定的。」他補充稱，如果金價較當前水平低20%，他會考慮。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a493dc65-dfaa-3cc0-9c52-c06ec037bab2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他還表示，隨著預測指向美國經濟將出現轉機，美元可能從當前水平走強，而這種變化可能會降低貴金屬的吸引力。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/t0UUtP773mpYttjLHlb6tQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/fbbcdc026cc2d021aac7a735105d200a\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他另外表示，中國、印度、韓國和台灣是該地區對全球投資者最具吸引力的股票市場。他補充說，由於中國在科技領域取得的進展，中國股市的上漲看起來具備可持續性。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"視頻：麥樸思談論他對市場的看法來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/v14XBnqg8sIQAwGozTv.Eg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/6cfe51142868ddc24730d75fb44591af\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">視頻：麥樸思談論他對市場的看法來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在開發中市場投資約三十年的麥樸思表示：「中國現在的目標是在科技領域、在高端晶片、在各種人工智能方面超越美國。資金正流向那個方向，而不是流向消費端。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他仍看好印度股市，並提到印度政府推動增加支出和投資，尤其是在科技領域。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Mobius Shuns Record-Breaking Gold on Risk of Dollar Rebound</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%BA%A5%E6%A8%B8%E6%80%9D%E7%A8%B1%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E9%87%91%E5%83%B9%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E5%8A%9B-%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2%E5%85%B7%E5%82%99%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%80%A7-093506028.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 20:56:05",
